Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.63,0:00:12.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.14,0:00:15.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就人類的性別來說是男性
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.72,0:00:19.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和動植物中的雄性是同義詞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.38,0:00:23.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在體現勇猛的情況下使用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.96,0:00:32.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇猛　嘿嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.99,0:02:07.96,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被邀請的　觀光者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.26,0:02:16.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千影小姐的家在懸崖那邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.25,0:02:19.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯　馬上就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.29,0:02:27.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是洋館
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.16,0:02:30.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這島上僅此一座
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.49,0:02:35.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說本來是為了漂流到這裡的西洋人而建造的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.72,0:02:39.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但想讓我看的東西是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.88,0:02:47.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了　我是行人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.07,0:02:49.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.74,0:02:54.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千影小姐有姐姐或者妹妹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.89,0:02:57.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.07,0:03:01.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　是指帕娜子小姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.03,0:03:04.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.70,0:03:10.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.84,0:03:12.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行…行人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.82,0:03:15.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.21,0:03:22.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.42,0:03:26.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.66,0:03:29.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人　沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.36,0:03:33.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了呢　行人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.73,0:03:36.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也讓我做各種觀察吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:41.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼得快點做歡迎的準備了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.50,0:03:43.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.71,0:03:47.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是在千影家做女傭的帕娜子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.93,0:03:50.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.24,0:03:52.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　真的不用介意了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.88,0:03:54.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕娜子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.16,0:03:59.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是公認的會照顧人脾氣又好　島上第一的美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.49,0:04:03.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,島上第一的美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.95,0:04:14.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行　想像的翅膀無法伸展
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.33,0:04:19.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,料理的手藝也很厲害　也許也是島上第一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.53,0:04:20.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.10,0:04:24.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要這樣　好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.00,0:04:29.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　我真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.22,0:04:32.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起　對不起　對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.94,0:04:34.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧　行人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.80,0:04:36.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.65,0:04:40.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕娜子小姐有時會不由自主的做些意外的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.34,0:04:45.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.23,0:04:49.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.59,0:04:52.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.98,0:04:54.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.58,0:04:59.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千影想讓人看的東西是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.69,0:05:05.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合適嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.11,0:05:11.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千影小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.81,0:05:13.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個打扮是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.72,0:05:16.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦　不喜歡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.35,0:05:18.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.69,0:05:22.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.27,0:05:23.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進了好的鮑魚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.63,0:05:29.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼　現在開始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.56,0:05:31.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:31.78,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.58,0:05:40.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人　如何
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.23,0:05:42.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連小鈴都
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.85,0:05:49.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺很有趣　但這個胸部有點緊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.57,0:05:51.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.84,0:05:55.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.40,0:05:58.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要被姐姐大人詛咒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:01.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.33,0:06:04.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說只是便裝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.84,0:06:06.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便裝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.03,0:06:10.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但怎麼想這都是最好的cosplay啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:14.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來　為什麼要穿成那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.92,0:06:19.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為書上說會讓行人高興
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.40,0:06:20.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.30,0:06:21.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是　在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.64,0:06:24.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廚師　熊貓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.53,0:06:27.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巫女　還有少婦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.77,0:06:31.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能參考這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.82,0:06:35.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是為什麼島上會有這種書
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.34,0:06:36.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　那是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.78,0:06:38.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴風雨來的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.10,0:06:44.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海浪常常會把漂流在島附近海外的東西吸進來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.10,0:07:05.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了剛才的書之外還有許多東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.42,0:07:07.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想讓行人看看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.81,0:07:09.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯　可以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.61,0:07:10.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫了大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.60,0:07:18.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂流過來的東西中最感興趣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.85,0:07:21.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是行人你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.83,0:07:23.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.40,0:07:29.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇　好多數量的書
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.81,0:07:32.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡的只是少數
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.71,0:07:36.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂流到藍蘭島上的書都在家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.93,0:07:39.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光這裡就象圖書館了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.75,0:07:42.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千影是島上最有知識的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.10,0:07:45.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還教過大家知識
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.28,0:07:49.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼　想讓我看的東西是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.81,0:07:52.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.50,0:07:54.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桶？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.56,0:07:56.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　是電飯煲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.73,0:07:58.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電…飯煲？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.59,0:08:01.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要把米放裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.18,0:08:03.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按下按鈕飯就做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.41,0:08:05.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.78,0:08:07.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要用火嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.68,0:08:10.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼　這個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.92,0:08:12.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是微波爐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.60,0:08:16.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把食物和飲料放進去按下按鈕就能變熱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.22,0:08:19.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種像金庫一樣的東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.68,0:08:21.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要火嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.28,0:08:22.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:27.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按這個按鈕…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.76,0:08:29.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說可能是很平常的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.20,0:08:33.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過對她們來說就像未知物體
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.26,0:08:37.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺有點新鮮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.59,0:08:40.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來到這島上一直都是我在吃驚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.55,0:08:45.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面的世界文明居然發展成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.60,0:08:48.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐　行人快點來用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.57,0:08:49.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個能做飯的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.10,0:08:54.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊　我也想看看如何工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.80,0:08:58.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.29,0:09:01.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這個島上沒有電吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.01,0:09:07.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個電是指能讓街燈發亮的erekitere發電機嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.53,0:09:08.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ereki…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.89,0:09:10.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛　差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.82,0:09:14.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的文明使用的物品沒有電是沒有用的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.64,0:09:18.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼在這裡的這些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.63,0:09:19.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.44,0:09:20.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.63,0:09:22.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些都…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.28,0:09:24.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯　只是垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.99,0:09:32.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　變白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.04,0:09:35.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是做了不好的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.74,0:09:38.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,垃…垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.31,0:09:40.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,垃圾房子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.82,0:09:44.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.71,0:09:48.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過只要知道了他們的真實情況就打住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.22,0:09:51.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然能做出這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.41,0:09:53.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面的文明真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.74,0:09:55.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼　差不多回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.59,0:09:57.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯　對呐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.09,0:09:59.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　要回去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.73,0:10:02.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯　因為還得做飯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.82,0:10:05.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.65,0:10:07.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過目的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.52,0:10:14.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　不好　關鍵的行人的觀察還沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.22,0:10:17.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…　等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.46,0:10:20.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意的話住下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.96,0:10:21.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住下來？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.91,0:10:22.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.84,0:10:23.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦　小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.79,0:10:26.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚飯也已經準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.40,0:10:30.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飯後的甜點也準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.32,0:10:31.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅豆大福
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.82,0:10:33.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅豆大福
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.96,0:10:37.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐　就接受邀請留下來吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.10,0:10:40.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嗎　行人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.27,0:10:43.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.04,0:10:45.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.03,0:10:47.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼請稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.22,0:10:56.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得好久沒有動手做料理
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.42,0:10:58.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要讓行人飽吃一頓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.05,0:11:02.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過說回來全是不可思議的料理呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.94,0:11:05.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漢堡包
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.95,0:11:06.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉麵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.16,0:11:09.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魚貝雞米飯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.16,0:11:09.16,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（燴肉飯上澆上含入魚貝，\N蘑菇的白色醬汁後在烤箱中烤制的菜肴）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.53,0:11:10.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶油麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.26,0:11:11.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃油
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.15,0:11:12.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鵝肝菜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.13,0:11:13.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅宋湯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.50,0:11:16.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不太知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.80,0:11:26.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建築是西式　果然食物也是西式吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.97,0:11:27.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西式？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.07,0:11:32.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　是指西洋的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.29,0:11:34.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會出來什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.59,0:11:35.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤蝦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.83,0:11:37.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海鮮火鍋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.95,0:11:39.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,義大利面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.99,0:11:42.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說咖哩飯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.47,0:11:49.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.66,0:11:53.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照行人所留下的島外的菜單所做的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.75,0:11:54.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.99,0:11:57.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那請吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.83,0:12:07.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…這是…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.79,0:12:09.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是漢堡包
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.23,0:12:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漢…漢堡包？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.37,0:12:12.05,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}煎餅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.37,0:12:12.05,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}菠菜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.92,0:12:16.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煎餅和豆腐真配
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.61,0:12:19.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃呢　這漢堡包
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.88,0:12:20.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.45,0:12:23.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼下面的料理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.00,0:12:25.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是拉麵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.92,0:12:27.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯　是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.77,0:12:29.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個看起來很像
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.78,0:12:31.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.52,0:12:37.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這面是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.55,0:12:44.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢　{\fnzhunyuan\fs27\b1}蒟蒻{\r}粉絲原來還有這種烏冬一樣的吃法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.64,0:12:49.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛　就像方便麵一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.41,0:12:53.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.44,0:12:54.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千影小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.55,0:12:55.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.51,0:12:56.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是章魚燒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.77,0:12:58.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,章魚燒？　好大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.94,0:13:06.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　動了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.02,0:13:08.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧　還是活的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.25,0:13:10.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把活章魚放進去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.59,0:13:11.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.63,0:13:12.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.93,0:13:20.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.70,0:13:22.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.44,0:13:24.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有這心意就很高興了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.55,0:13:28.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就去做些其他東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.34,0:13:30.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.62,0:13:32.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通的飯就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.45,0:13:34.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通　比如？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.07,0:13:38.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢　像咖哩飯一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.64,0:13:41.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這島上沒有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.75,0:13:44.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魚咖哩就不是飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.43,0:13:46.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的　咖哩飯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.41,0:13:47.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.35,0:13:49.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個很辣的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.75,0:13:51.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不擅長吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.23,0:13:53.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.78,0:13:55.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有咖哩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.43,0:13:56.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.84,0:14:01.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖哩飯是在「文明開化」的時候進入日本的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.43,0:14:05.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖哩原來是那麼有歷史的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.80,0:14:08.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼　一份咖哩飯就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.11,0:14:10.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.84,0:14:15.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇　咖哩飯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.82,0:14:17.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.75,0:14:23.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何　合你口味嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.99,0:14:30.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…太…好吃了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.54,0:14:32.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.69,0:14:35.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好辣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.56,0:14:36.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.89,0:14:39.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅豆大福
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.14,0:14:44.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯　真幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.95,0:14:50.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒想到能在這島上吃到咖哩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.73,0:14:54.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧　時間過得比預想的要快
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.02,0:14:57.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼還是回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.28,0:14:59.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在…在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.93,0:15:02.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.29,0:15:04.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且家裡攢了許多衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.96,0:15:08.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行　現在才是正式的觀察
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.04,0:15:10.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觀察？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.18,0:15:11.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正式是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.60,0:15:14.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.01,0:15:17.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.02,0:15:23.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話　就算強硬手段也要讓他們住下來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.95,0:15:27.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　章魚在頭上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.22,0:15:33.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦　對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.44,0:15:35.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.76,0:15:40.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請吧　這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.50,0:15:41.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.04,0:16:00.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就…在你們兩個洗好後進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.62,0:16:11.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人一直都不和我一起洗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.96,0:16:13.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.43,0:16:15.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還一直噴鼻血
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.12,0:16:17.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.50,0:16:20.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是出乎計算之外
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.57,0:16:24.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來還打算在為行人擦背的時候做各種調查
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.54,0:16:29.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了　還有其他手段
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.15,0:16:31.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜晚還很長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.80,0:16:44.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣泡著　只會增大對行人的探知心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.72,0:16:45.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,增大…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.79,0:16:55.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾在別人家裡洗澡也好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.62,0:16:57.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.62,0:17:00.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了　千影
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.41,0:17:04.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起探知心來了　對小鈴胸部的急速成長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.78,0:17:08.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也已經非常在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.47,0:17:10.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那手是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.93,0:17:14.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便讓我來調查一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.38,0:17:23.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪天真的會死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.82,0:17:28.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人　洗好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.83,0:17:30.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.46,0:17:45.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨大的浴室真舒爽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.18,0:17:48.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.21,0:17:53.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能一起進去的話　那就偷窺好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.06,0:17:57.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過沒有眼睛好難看清
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.68,0:17:59.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠近點看的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.68,0:18:10.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.09,0:18:16.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我來幫你擦背吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.53,0:18:18.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　帕娜子小姐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.88,0:18:19.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.11,0:18:21.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.45,0:18:25.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎　那麼拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.41,0:18:30.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕娜子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.74,0:18:35.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人不介意帕娜子小姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.09,0:18:37.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我和小鈴卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.91,0:18:43.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.84,0:18:45.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.66,0:18:48.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機會　帕娜子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.86,0:18:49.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.97,0:18:52.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁機調查行人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.51,0:18:58.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圓滑的男生輪廓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.33,0:19:01.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯的肌肉體質
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.07,0:19:04.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸部也還可以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.93,0:19:07.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是男人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.98,0:19:11.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了　忽然心跳加速了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.75,0:19:13.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是泡的太長了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.55,0:19:15.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝　帕娜子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.85,0:19:21.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　好險
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.76,0:19:29.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然在遠處看不清
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.59,0:19:31.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有點危險…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.11,0:19:41.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕佳的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.48,0:19:58.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕娜子小姐也來泡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.14,0:19:59.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.10,0:20:11.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕娜子小姐應該安靜點進來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.85,0:20:13.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.09,0:20:34.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千…千影
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.38,0:20:40.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好重
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.41,0:20:42.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.80,0:20:43.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是泡久了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.85,0:20:45.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就會好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.98,0:20:48.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果還是住下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.34,0:20:51.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.36,0:20:56.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了什麼讓小鈴生氣的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.69,0:21:01.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在浴室　就把我當做沒必要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.58,0:21:06.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是　我完全不知道千影躲在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.15,0:21:08.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕娜子小姐不也一起了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.00,0:21:11.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯　怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.30,0:21:16.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來行人說男人和女人洗澡要分開是騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.97,0:21:19.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕娜子小姐是大象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.14,0:21:22.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管大象還是人　女孩子就是女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.03,0:21:26.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的　在和我一起洗澡之前不原諒你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.08,0:21:29.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.28,0:22:55.03,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&HE7A573}「想要迷惑他…繼承人」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.76,0:23:04.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.11,0:23:07.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類性別來說是男性
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.39,0:23:10.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又和動植物中的雄性同義詞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.55,0:23:14.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在體現勇敢勇猛的情況下使用
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.34,0:23:18.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謎團越來越多了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.98,0:23:22.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人　接下來也讓我繼續調查吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.61,0:23:28.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有去洗澡也會頭暈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.50,0:23:32.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個謎團
